HEADWORD: Dissertate
<hw>Dis"ser*tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>dissertatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>dissertare</ets> to discuss,
intents, fr. <ets>disserere</ets>. See <er>Dissert</er>.]</ety> <def>To
deal in dissertation; to write dissertations; to discourse.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>J. Foster.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
